M||tx|---
M||titl|cr Explicit cp Variants
M||impa|md
M||impa|self-documenting code, no hidden conditionals
M||tags|composition, variants, architecture
M||tx|---
M|Crea|tx|Instead of one cp w/ many boolean props, cr explicit variant
M|Crea|tx|cp. Each variant composes the pieces it needs. The code documents
M|Crea|tx|itself.
M|Crea|**In|**
M|Crea|tx|```tsx
M|Crea|tx|// What does this cp actually render?
M|Crea|tx|<Composer
M|Crea|tx|isThread
M|Crea|tx|isEditing={false}
M|Crea|tx|channelId='abc'
M|Crea|tx|showAttachments
M|Crea|tx|showFormatting={false}
M|Crea|tx|/>
M|Crea|tx|```
M|Crea|**Co|**
M|Crea|tx|```tsx
M|Crea|tx|// Immediately clear what this renders
M|Crea|tx|<ThreadComposer channelId="abc" />
M|Crea|tx|// Or
M|Crea|tx|<EditMessageComposer messageId="xyz" />
M|Crea|tx|// Or
M|Crea|tx|<ForwardMessageComposer messageId="123" />
M|Crea|tx|```
M|Crea|tx|Each implementation is unique, explicit and self-contained. Yet they can each
M|Crea|tx|use shared parts.
M|Crea|**Im|**
M|Crea|tx|```tsx
M|Crea|func|{ channelId: string }) {
M|Crea|tx|return (
M|Crea|tx|<ThreadProvider channelId={channelId}>
M|Crea|tx|<Composer.Frame>
M|Crea|tx|<Composer.Input />
M|Crea|tx|<AlsoSendToChannelField channelId={channelId} />
M|Crea|tx|<Composer.Footer>
M|Crea|tx|<Composer.Formatting />
M|Crea|tx|<Composer.Emojis />
M|Crea|tx|<Composer.Submit />
M|Crea|tx|</Composer.Footer>
M|Crea|tx|</Composer.Frame>
M|Crea|tx|</ThreadProvider>
M|Crea|tx|)
M|Crea|tx|}
M|Crea|func|{ messageId: string }) {
M|Crea|tx|return (
M|Crea|tx|<EditMessageProvider messageId={messageId}>
M|Crea|tx|<Composer.Frame>
M|Crea|tx|<Composer.Input />
M|Crea|tx|<Composer.Footer>
M|Crea|tx|<Composer.Formatting />
M|Crea|tx|<Composer.Emojis />
M|Crea|tx|<Composer.CancelEdit />
M|Crea|tx|<Composer.SaveEdit />
M|Crea|tx|</Composer.Footer>
M|Crea|tx|</Composer.Frame>
M|Crea|tx|</EditMessageProvider>
M|Crea|tx|)
M|Crea|tx|}
M|Crea|func|{ messageId: string }) {
M|Crea|tx|return (
M|Crea|tx|<ForwardMessageProvider messageId={messageId}>
M|Crea|tx|<Composer.Frame>
M|Crea|tx|<Composer.Input placeholder="Add a message, if you'd like." />
M|Crea|tx|<Composer.Footer>
M|Crea|tx|<Composer.Formatting />
M|Crea|tx|<Composer.Emojis />
M|Crea|tx|<Composer.Mentions />
M|Crea|tx|</Composer.Footer>
M|Crea|tx|</Composer.Frame>
M|Crea|tx|</ForwardMessageProvider>
M|Crea|tx|)
M|Crea|tx|}
M|Crea|tx|```
M|Crea|Each|
M|Crea|it|What pr/state it uses
M|Crea|it|What UI elements it includes
M|Crea|it|What actions are available
M|Crea|tx|No boolean prop combinations to reason abt. No impossible states.